select_statement(all_rows,[qualified(identifier('ANALYSIS'),identifier('SADATE')),qualified(identifier('ANALYSIS'),identifier('SACUST')),qualified(identifier('ANALYSIS'),identifier('SAREF')),qualified(identifier('ANALYSIS'),identifier('SAPRODUCT')),qualified(identifier('ANALYSIS'),identifier('SAORGQTY')),qualified(identifier('ANALYSIS'),identifier('SACOST')),qualified(identifier('ANALYSIS'),identifier('SAVAL'))],[table(catalog_qualified(identifier('NISAINT_CS'),identifier('ANALYSIS')),identifier('ANALYSIS'))],[where(in(qualified(identifier('ANALYSIS'),identifier('SAREF')),subselect(select_statement(distinct,[identifier('SAREF')],[table(identifier('ANALYSIS'),no_alias)],[where(like(identifier('SAPRODUCT'),string_literal('4K0%')))]))))]).
